atches, racking up points that ultimately led to their victory.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Robo Swan team\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"their matches\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"points\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"their victory\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The finals were done in a round-robin format with all four teams playing each other.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The finals\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"a round-robin format\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"all four teams\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to taking the overall prize, Robo Swan also won other special awards for highest robot run, robot kaizen or continuous improvement, and the most consistent robot.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Chrono_Trigger\", \"score\": 0.995315347989537, \"rank\": 0.004706701267552609, \"text\": \"Robo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Chrono_Trigger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Chrono_Trigger\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall prize\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"other special awards\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"highest robot run\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"robot kaizen\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"continuous improvement\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"the most consistent robot\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RoboFlash from Mona Prep, though not a finalist, won the benevolence excellence award.\", \"from\": 136